關係，下篇繼續。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"六月份篇文章<br />\n<br />\n睇淡AAPL<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有貨"},{"pid":"69343d2a97b8168d9fb0dc96e247a58e820826e5","tid":1695770,"uid":186800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"044f2fa10325959ddb5d5471f4b8f687e2dfe0e0","tid":1695770,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23979b5e26d56eacaaabe5e2ed7dfcd8e9ce2d3b","tid":1695770,"uid":186800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"6033 sun mobile? 我有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fb4afc2a0df75b2395de649ec6166ae2968b42","tid":1695770,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd3d8e308cf99c4154b2c5f2346d63e57ee03f9","tid":1695770,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0a58e29e51b268e132a1f6f142e6697522a649","tid":1695770,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e09a5820a967bced81fd27478076d1f69979539","tid":1695770,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:54:18.000Z","msg":"【淺入股票投資：乜嘢係折現（Discounting）？】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/567419136975056/posts/990237088026590?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F567419136975056%2Fposts%2F990237088026590%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=17667e3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/567419136975056/posts/990237088026590?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n投資股票，其實就等於買入一檔生意，但到底要用幾多錢來買入這